snippet.title: Witchblood - Trailer [VR, Oculus Rift]
snippet.description:
Trailer for Witchblood, a virtual reality metroidvania game set in a diorama world. Developed by Hidden Path Entertainment, available for Oculus Rift. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/witchblood
